__Artist's Statement:__ I first learned of zines from the Davis Enterprise when the Davis Art Center had an article of things to do with children during pandemic. So my zines have all been done either walking on campus or in my neighborhood at the Haagen Dasz bee haven or at home drawing fruits and veggies or my cat Minette.
